.B \-c=CURSOR\-BLINK, \-\-cursor-blink=CURSOR\-BLINK
Set cursor blink mode.
Type: BOOL.
.
.TP
.B \-G=VISUAL\-BELL, \-\-visual\-bell=VISUAL\-BELL
Set visual bell mode.
Type: BOOL.
.
.TP
.B \-F, \-\-fullscreen
Go into the fullscreen mode from start.
