.
.TP
.B Ctrl+Shift+Home
Bring up "tab" switcher.
.
.TP
.B Ctrl+Shift+PgUp
Split terminal horizontally (one terminal above the other).
.
.TP
.B Ctrl+Shift+PgDn
Split terminal vertically (one terminal to the left of the other).
.
